WEBVTT

00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:09.980
=Rise of Her Lady Physician=

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:12.340
=Episode 23=

00:00:12.380 --> 00:00:14.940
=Do You Like Me?=

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:16.800
After I discovered the problem,

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:18.430
I secretly asked Officer Song to

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:19.760
replace the water you used

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:21.560
for making tea and tonic soup

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:23.520
with water boiled in a copper pot.

00:00:24.680 --> 00:00:25.880
Look at you,

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:27.160
your hair is falling out.

00:00:27.880 --> 00:00:29.520
How dare you say it's not poisonous?

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:31.630
Nonsense!

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:32.520
Nonsense!

00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:33.780
I just...

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:35.360
I just caught a cold!

00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:37.240
Your Majesty, I just caught a cold,

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:38.960
and my hair fell out.

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:41.880
Cold, huh?

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:43.560
It's okay to only drink water

00:00:43.720 --> 00:00:44.640
boiled in a copper pot.

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:46.960
But once mixed with herbs or tea,

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:49.280
it'll alter their medicinal properties.

00:00:49.960 --> 00:00:51.160
You're a healthy person,

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:53.440
yet you've lost hair due to
chronic poisoning

00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:56.400
from drinking such tea every day,

00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:59.080
let alone the Princess Consort,
who was pregnant and weak.

00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:01.040
That is why the fetus was disturbed.

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:02.600
Your Majesty, I'm innocent!

00:01:03.080 --> 00:01:04.000
I'm innocent!

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:06.400
Do you think His Majesty will believe

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:08.080
a mere medical attendant?

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:10.760
I-I'm innocent!

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.400
This lowly servant did it herself!

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:14.720
It has nothing to do with me!

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:17.640
I'm innocent, Your Majesty!

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:18.960
Feng Mingyuan,

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.600
what is done by night

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:21.920
appears by day.

00:01:22.310 --> 00:01:23.160
No, Your Majesty...

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:24.000
Shut up!

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:26.240
Feng Mingyuan,

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:28.200
why did you attempt to harm my grandson?

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:29.640
Who ordered you to do this?

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:33.280
Your Majesty, I'm innocent!

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.120
Guards!

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:36.280
Drag him down

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:37.720
and torture him!

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:39.320
– Aye!
– Your Majesty!

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:40.600
Your Majesty, I'm innocent!

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:42.760
- Get off me!
- Go!

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:43.840
Get off me!

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:56.840
No one can judge me!

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:08.600
He's dead!

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:09.480
Oh my god!

00:02:16.120 --> 00:02:17.000
Mingyuan...

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:25.040
Here's my decree.

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:26.960
Feng Mingyuan

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.800
harmed the imperial heir

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:30.240
and deserved his death!

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:32.360
The Feng family will be executed,

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:34.600
and all persons involved in the case

00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:36.040
shall be strictly investigated

00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:37.570
and punished

00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:38.440
according to the law!

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:08.840
Mingyuan...

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.640
We've known each other since childhood.

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:17.080
You loved me so much.

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.560
Sorry, I've failed you.

00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:29.600
It's all Rong Zelan's fault!

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:35.240
Back then, her mother ruined my plan.

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:40.360
And you died because of her.

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:47.160
I must make her pay!

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:53.600
I will crush her into mud

00:03:55.880 --> 00:03:57.880
like I did to her mother!

00:04:19.200 --> 00:04:20.040
Rong Zelan!

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:25.440
Rong Zelan!

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.440
What happened?

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:31.440
Are you okay?

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:33.680
Wake up!

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:38.080
Summon the physician!

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:41.240
Zelan...

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:44.920
Danger and traps

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:47.440
prevail in the palace.

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:49.320
I worry about you every day.

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:53.480
Every time I see you taking risks alone,

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:55.240
I fear that

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:56.560
I'd never see you again.

00:05:00.040 --> 00:05:00.880
I can't believe

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:04.120
it has happened after all.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.720
Zelan...

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:10.560
Zelan,

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.560
I'm sorry!

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:17.640
Song Lingxiao?

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:21.240
I'm...

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:22.920
out of breath.

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:24.200
You're okay?

00:05:26.040 --> 00:05:29.160
I just drank some plum wine
and fell asleep.

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:31.000
So, it's just

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:33.520
plum wine.

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:37.080
Yes.

00:05:38.920 --> 00:05:39.760
Plum wine is good.

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:44.000
You're still alive.

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:56.200
It's surprising that plum wine

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:58.280
could do this to you.

00:05:59.640 --> 00:06:01.240
Do you like me?

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:08.640
I thought even the magpies in the garden

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:12.960
could tell it
from the way I look at you.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:14.640
Really?

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:16.600
Why can't I tell it?

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:25.040
It seems

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:29.080
I should make it more obvious.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:35.840
Sober up.

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:46.000
Rong Zelan.

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:48.440
I know you want to become

00:06:49.440 --> 00:06:50.280
an imperial physician

00:06:50.280 --> 00:06:51.240
and clear your mother's name.

00:06:52.440 --> 00:06:53.880
However, the road is full of thorns.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:04.840
Rong Zelan,

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:06.840
are you willing

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.080
to have a companion with you

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:10.640
on this road

00:07:11.080 --> 00:07:12.200
full of thorns?

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.080
He can be your guard.

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:19.040
He can cut through thorns

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.160
and shield you from storms.

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:39.240
Your Majesty,

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:42.160
this morning, I saw the peonies
in the garden blooming brilliantly.

00:07:42.320 --> 00:07:44.400
It is thanks to the blessings
of a prosperous country.

00:07:45.160 --> 00:07:46.120
Mother, I couldn't have

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:48.200
made it without your wisdom.

00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:50.520
Jiangnan has seen
great harvest this year.

00:07:50.840 --> 00:07:51.960
Everything's good in the palace.

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:53.200
Ancestors have blessed us.

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:54.360
Indeed.

00:08:03.600 --> 00:08:04.440
Well,

00:08:04.640 --> 00:08:06.040
my little grandson is here.

00:08:07.880 --> 00:08:08.720
Oh.

00:08:09.200 --> 00:08:10.060
Your Majesty,

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:10.960
look,

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:17.840
he's adorable.

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:22.880
Father,

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:24.480
I have a request.

00:08:24.880 --> 00:08:26.120
Could you please allow it?

00:08:26.800 --> 00:08:27.640
Speak freely.

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:30.280
Having gone through this crisis,

00:08:30.640 --> 00:08:32.640
I've realized the hardships
of women in the palace.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.280
Due to gender restrictions,

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:36.120
it's inconvenient for us

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.480
to consult a male physician

00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:38.320
sometimes,

00:08:38.840 --> 00:08:40.320
thus the illness is often delayed,

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.400
causing much trouble.

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:43.280
I boldly ask you

00:08:44.040 --> 00:08:45.200
to consider

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:46.720
having a female physician

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:49.000
who can provide consultations
for the women in the palace.

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:53.500
Your Majesty.

00:08:53.520 --> 00:08:55.120
The Princess Consort is right.

00:08:57.840 --> 00:08:58.680
Your Majesty.

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:00.240
It's inappropriate to

00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:01.400
have a female officer.

00:09:01.880 --> 00:09:02.720
Moreover,

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:04.160
there's no precedent

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:06.800
for a female official
throughout history.

00:09:14.520 --> 00:09:15.360
Mother,

00:09:15.520 --> 00:09:16.440
what do you think.

00:09:17.880 --> 00:09:18.960
It's embarrassing

00:09:19.400 --> 00:09:20.800
to discuss our privacy

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:21.920
with a male physician.

00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:24.360
Your Majesty.

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:26.800
I remember you once promised

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.320
to allow Attendant Rong

00:09:28.600 --> 00:09:30.960
to legally make diagnoses
and prescribe medicine

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:32.880
if she can prove her innocence

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:36.160
in the poisoning case
of the Princess Consort.

00:09:36.760 --> 00:09:37.720
Given this,

00:09:37.800 --> 00:09:39.080
if she's not a medical officer,

00:09:39.400 --> 00:09:40.520
how could her work be legal?

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.480
Attendant Rong

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:43.560
is skilled in medicine.

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:48.000
She saved the Princess Consort
and your grandson

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:51.320
and cured the little princess and me.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:54.680
In my opinion,

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:55.960
Your Majesty,

00:09:56.760 --> 00:09:58.160
it is time to fulfill that promise.